# Content (`src/content/**`)

- Collections: `blog`, `authors`, `podcast`, `legal` under `src/content/<name>/`.
- Built by `scripts/build-content.mjs` → `src/generated/*.json` (run via `npm run content` / prestart / prebuild).
- **Do not change frontmatter fields** without updating the content builder and every consumer in `lib/content.ts` / `app/`.
- **`blog`:** Required: `title`, `slug`, `pubDate`, `description`, `heroImage`, `tags` (`culture|atlas|history|persona|power`). Optional: `draft`, `author`. Body is HTML.
- **Templates:** `src/content/blog/anime.md`, `authors/juliet-ramos.md`, `podcast/1.md`, `legal/privacy.md`.
- Author/podcast image URLs under `/src/images/...` are rewritten to `/images/...` and copied into `public/images/` by the content builder.
